data.description: Here is the opportunity to own this home in Brick, just a short distance from local shopping and the water. The home welcomes you with a large open living room featuring an oversized from window. The living room leads to the dining room with sliding door to the porch to entertain guests. The kitchen welcomes you with room for an eat in kitchen area for the family with a bonus room on the first floor for your choice of use. The three bedrooms are just up the stairs with a shared all tile full bathroom. Take a trip over to the home for yourself.
